    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This *+1 striking flintlock musket* features multiple triangular panels that can be folded out of the stock, like the petals of a tigridia flower, that collect sunlight and feed it into the spark gun's core. All damage dealt by a *solar shellflower* is fire damage.",
